'''ISO 3166-2:MG''' codes for the [[provinces of Madagascar]]. The purpose of this family of standards is to establish a worldwide series of short abbreviations for places, for use on package labels, containers and such. Anywhere where a short alphanumeric code can serve to clearly indicate a location in a more convenient and less ambiguous form than the full place name. 

== Provinces (10) ==
* MG-A	[[Toamasina Province|Toamasina]]
* MG-D	[[Antsiranana Province|Antsiranana]]
* MG-F	[[Fianarantsoa Province|Fianarantsoa]]
* MG-M	[[Mahajanga Province|Mahajanga]]
* MG-T	[[Antananarivo Province|Antananarivo]]
* MG-U	[[Toliara Province|Toliara]]


